# Testing

## Unit tests (Vitest)

- Live in `tests/`; name `{module}.test.ts`.
- Cover engine and store logic — grader, SRS, queues, progress, registry.
- Run: `npm run test`

## E2E (Playwright)

- Live in `e2e/`; smoke-test critical navigation flows.
- Use HUD titles from `HudHeader` (`Command Overview`, not legacy names).
- Dev server starts automatically via `playwright.config.ts`.
- Run: `npm run test:e2e`

## Content validation

- Every lesson and capstone must pass Zod schemas.
- Run: `npm run validate-content` after editing content files.

## Before merge

```bash
npm run build && npm run test && npm run validate-content && npm run lint && npm run test:e2e
```
